{"lemma": "أَرْضٌ", "slug": "أَرْضٌ", "root": "#.ر.ض", "root_slug": "_-ر-ض", "root_link": "/words/roots/_-ر-ض", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": true, "lemma_key": "أَرْض", "root": "أرض", "pos": "N", "occurrence_count": 461}, "wiktextract": {"found": true, "entry_count": 1, "pos_tags": ["verb"], "has_etymology": false, "sense_count": 0}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n573", "n3164", "n576", "n580", "n15703", "n15711"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B6%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "earth", "fa": "زمین", "ur": "زمین", "tr": "yer", "id": "bumi", "bn": "পৃথিবী", "es": "tierra", "fr": "terre", "de": "Erde", "ru": "земля", "zh": "大地"}, "definition": null, "etymology": null, "ipa": null, "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n573", "headword_ar": "اَرْضٌ", "root": "Ar$", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "making mischief;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "exciting disorder, disturbance, disagreement, discord, dissension, strife,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "quarrelling;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taA^oriy$N", "text_ar": "تَاْرِيشٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; see 2, and see also 1;] syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fasaAdN", "text_ar": "فَسَادٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[in the sense of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ifosaAdN", "text_ar": "اـِفْسَادٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; (Msb;) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_igoraA='N", "text_ar": "اـِغْرَا=ءٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (K.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Disagreement, discord,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "dissension; and contention,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "altercation:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "you say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayonahumaA A^aro$N", "text_ar": "بَيْنَهُمَا اَرْشٌ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Between them two is disagreement,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c. (K.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A fine,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mulct, for a wound:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Mgh, Msb, K:) from the first of the significations in this paragraph; (Msb;) or from its being one of the causes of contention, or altercation; or, accord. to AM, from the same word as inf. n. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aruw$N", "text_ar": "اَرُوشٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the first of the senses explained in this art.; accord. to IF, originally"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "haro$N", "text_ar": "هَرْشٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^uruw$N", "text_ar": "اُرُوشٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (Mgh, Msb.) Hence the saying mentioned by IAar,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AinotaZironiY Hat~aY", "text_ar": "اِنْتَظِرْنِى حَتَّى"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taEoqila falayosa laka EinodanaA A^aro$N A_il~aA AlA^asin~apu", "text_ar": "تَعْقِلَ فَلَيْسَ لَكَ عِنْدَنَا اَرْشٌ اـِلَّا الاَسِنَّةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Wait thou for me until thou accept a fine for a wound in lieu of retaliation; for thou hast no compensation for a wound to receive from us except the spearheads"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: meaning, thou shalt not slay a man for whom we will ever give bloodwit. (L, TA.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "What is diminished"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the price"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by reason of a defect in a garment"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "piece of cloth:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as being a cause of contention, or altercation. (K, * TA.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "What is payed"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by way of adjustment of the difference"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "between freedom from defect and defect in an article of merchandise:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Kt, K:) for when the purchaser of a garment or piece of cloth as being free from defect discovers in it a hole or other defect, contention ensues between him and the seller. (TA.) ―         -b4-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A bribe."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Aboo-Nahshal, Sh, K.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "Mgh", "Msb", "K", "TA", "Kt"]}, {"entry_id": "n3164", "headword_ar": "اَرْضٌ", "root": "bld", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ": (S, TA: [a meaning assigned in the K to"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baladN", "text_ar": "بَلَدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; but this appears to be a mistake occasioned by the accidental omission of the word"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlbalodapN", "text_ar": "البَلْدَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":]) you say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*ihi balodatunaA", "text_ar": "هٰذِهِ بَلْدَتُنَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "This is our land,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.] like as you say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*ihi baHoratunaA", "text_ar": "هٰذِهِ بَحْرَتُنَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S, TA:) the pl. (of the former, S, Msb) is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bulodaAnN", "text_ar": "بُلْدَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, Msb) and (of the same, S, or of the latter, Msb)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bilaAdN", "text_ar": "بِلَادٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (T, S, M, Msb:) [which latter, regarded as pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "balodapN", "text_ar": "بَلْدَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in a more limited sense than"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baladN", "text_ar": "بَلَدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", is often used as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "provinces collectively;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a country:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bulodaAnN", "text_ar": "بُلْدَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "syn. with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kuwarN", "text_ar": "كُوَرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[which signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "districts,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "tracts of country; quarters,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "regions;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and also,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "cities, towns,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "villages"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (T.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Albaladu", "text_ar": "البَلَدُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Albalodapu", "text_ar": "البَلْدَةُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "are names applied to"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Mekkeh;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K;) in like manner as"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aln~ajomu", "text_ar": "النَّجْمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is a name applied to the Pleiades. (M.) [So too"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Albaladu AlA^amiynu", "text_ar": "البَلَدُ الاَمِينُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Albaladu", "text_ar": "البَلَدُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlHaraAmu", "text_ar": "الحَرَامُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baladN may~itN", "text_ar": "بَلَدٌ مَيِّتٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A tract of land without herbage,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pasture:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baladN", "text_ar": "بَلَدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "alone,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "desert, a waterless desert,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "such as is termed"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mafaAzapK", "text_ar": "مَفَازَةٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA voce"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tA", "text_ar": "تا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; under which see an ex.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baladN", "text_ar": "بَلَدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Land which has not been dug, and upon which fire has not been kindled."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "house,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "dwelling, such as is termed"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "dAr", "text_ar": "دار"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (M, K:) of the dial. of ElYemen. (M.) Sb mentions the saying,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*ihi Ald~aAru", "text_ar": "هٰذِهِ الدَّارُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "niEomati Albaladu", "text_ar": "نِعْمَتِ البَلَدُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "This house, excellent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "most excel-lent, is the dwelling!"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; in which"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Albld", "text_ar": "البلد"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is made fem. because it is syn. with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AldAr", "text_ar": "الدار"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (M.) ―         -b4-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A burial-ground:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K:) or, as some say, (M, but in the K “and,”)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a grave,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sepulchre:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K:) pl. as above. (M.) ―         -b5-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Dust,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "earth;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and so ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yalodapN", "text_ar": "يَلْدَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (T, M, K.) ―         -b6-  The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "place in which an ostrich lays its egg, in sand."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, L, K.) And hence,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayoDapu Albaladi", "text_ar": "بَيْضَةُ البَلَدِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The egg of the ostrich, which it abandons in the place where it lays it, in the sand,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in a desert:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, L:) also called ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Albaladiy~api", "text_ar": "البَلَدِيَّةِ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "*aAtu Albaladi", "text_ar": "ذَاتُ البَلَدِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (M.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fulaAnN bayoDapu Albaladi", "text_ar": "فُلَانٌ بَيْضَةُ البَلَدِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one is"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "like"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the egg of the ostrich,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.], meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "such a one is unequalled,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "unparalleled:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "said in dispraise and in praise: (M, * L:) allowed by A'Obeyd to be used in praise: and said by El-Bekree to be applied to him who is separated from his family and near relations. (TA.) [See also art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "byD", "text_ar": "بيض"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".] You also say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "huwa A^a*al~u mino bayoDapi", "text_ar": "هُوَ اَذَلُّ مِنْ بَيْضَةِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Albaladi", "text_ar": "البَلَدِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, A) (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He is more object,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "vile, than the egg of the ostrich, which it abandons"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, TA)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the desert, and to which it does not return."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) [See again art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "byD", "text_ar": "بيض"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".] Also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "huwa A^aEaz~a mino", "text_ar": "هُوَ اَعَزَّ مِنْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayoDapi Albaladi", "text_ar": "بَيْضَةِ البَلَدِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He is more highly esteemed than the egg of the ostrich, which it lays in the sand"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; because the ostrich spreads its wings over it and sits upon it. (A in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "frx", "text_ar": "فرخ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) [See more in art."}], "source_refs": ["S", "TA", "M", "Msb", "T", "K", "L", "A"]}, {"entry_id": "n576", "headword_ar": "ارّض", "root": "ArD", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", (TK,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taA^oriyDN", "text_ar": "تَاْرِيضٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He depastured the herbage of the earth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "land:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he sought after it:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) or, accord. to some,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taA^oriyDN", "text_ar": "تَاْرِيضٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "denotes this latter signification with respect to a place of alighting, or abiding: (TA:) and you say [also],"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Almanozila", "text_ar": "المَنْزِلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tA^r~D", "text_ar": "تارّض", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he sought after, and chose, the place for alighting,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "abiding:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, TA:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lilomanozili", "text_ar": "لِلْمَنْزِلِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tarakotu AlHaY~a yataA^ar~aDuwna", "text_ar": "تَرَكْتُ الحَىَّ يَتَاَرَّضُونَ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I left the tribe seeking after a tract of country in which to alight,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "abide."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it, rendered heavy;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[app. meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "slow,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sluggish;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "see 5;] syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "vaq~ala", "text_ar": "ثَقَّلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (Ibn-'Abbád, K.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made to tarry; to tarry and wait,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "expect;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to be patient, and tarry, and wait,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "expect."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ibn- 'Abbád, K.)"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 48}], "source_refs": ["TK", "K", "TA", "M"]}, {"entry_id": "n580", "headword_ar": "اَرَضٌ", "root": "ArD", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ": see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^araDapN", "text_ar": "اَرَضَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": []}, {"entry_id": "n15703", "headword_ar": "ارضّ", "root": "rD", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iroDaADN", "text_ar": "اـِرْضَاضٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a man, S)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, heavy and slow."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K.) And"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He ran vehemently."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(ISk, K.) Thus it has two contr. significations. (K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ArD~ fiY AlA^aroDi", "text_ar": "ارضّ فِى الاَرْضِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He went away into the country,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the land;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "*ahaba", "text_ar": "ذَهَبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[q. v.]. (ISk, TA.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ArD~t Alr~aviyoy^apu", "text_ar": "ارضّت الرَّثِيْيَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, K,) inf. n. as above, (S,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "milk termed"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rvyy^p", "text_ar": "رثيية"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became thick."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ArD~ AlEaraqa", "text_ar": "ارضّ العَرَقَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(fatigue, TA, or food or drink, AZ, K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "made the sweat to flow."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AZ, * K, * TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "K", "TA"]}, {"entry_id": "n15711", "headword_ar": "اَرَضُّ", "root": "rD", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Always sitting still, not quitting his place."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ibn-'Abbád, K.)"}], "source_refs": []}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}